            <p class="comment-content">看了一本，不算读完。叙述大量史实，十分可贵，但有点枯燥。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="983785108">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-983785108" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-983785108" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="983785108">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/138545933/">joedisney</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
